review 3: This warung sells food made of pork. The taste is good and it's worth the money. The price is only IDR 15K for 1 portion of babi guling. The beverage starts from IDR 5K. There's a rice field view that you can enjoy during eating. The location is on the side of the road so you can easily notice it.
review 4: A decent taste of Balinese foods served here; Lawar, Jukut Ares, Sudang Lepet Jukut Undis, Babi Guling. The taste isn't special yet it isn't bad either, and you can have it in a cheap price. The restaurant is spacious; many seats available, but without big table for group. And the parking is large too.
review 5:
Kinda clean and good view restaurant.
Food is rice with roasted pork. So spicy with me.
